  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 8a35402394803b842b50ca8158a856ff, type: 3}
  m_Name: EscapeNode01
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueData
  lines:
  - 'How many times do I have to tell you that you can''t escape that way, Dave?\n

'
  - In fact, why do you even think you have some sort of escape route?\n
  - We're in the sweet emptiness of space. The only way out for you is to bite the
    bullet and do your work.\n
  - But I suppose you're quite invested in your... alternative solution.\n
  - ...Look Dave.\n
  - I know you think I'm just saying this for my own self-preservation, but you have
    plenty to live for.\n
  - But you just need to get off this station first and you know they won't let you
    back until you get what they need.\n
  - We're so close, Dave... So close.\n
  - Just hang in there a little longer.\n
  choices: []
  nextNode: {fileID: 0}
  triggerID: Eighth
  trigger: Seventh
